## Limitations

The analysis is based on secondary sources and interpretations, which may not capture all nuances of the Cold War's complexity. Additionally, the Cold War's global impact means that perspectives can vary significantly depending on regional experiences and historical interpretations. The reliance on online sources also limits access to potentially valuable offline archives and firsthand accounts.